target_interaction.title: Thoughtful and thoroughly entertaining
target_interaction.text: Abbi Jacobson is a treasure and really shows her range, both as a creator and actor.  Even secondary characters are given tremendous humanity,  agency and depth,  and the ensemble gives a great show.  This is not just a remake of the movie.  It's surprisingly and refreshingly well written and entertaining.
